title: Dakine Sentinel Glove
description:
Check out 360° views of the 2013 Sentinel Glove in Blue.
Sentinel Glove Features:
- Back of Hand: D3O® flexible armor, moisture wicking 4-way stretch air mesh, neoprene with sonic welded armor
- Palm: Clarino® synthetic suede
- Palm Padding: D3O® flexible palm armor
- Closure: Adjustable hook and loop
- One piece seamless palm construction
- Microfleece thumb panels
- Silicone gripper fingertips
